<h1>DSKI Makers Camp 2019</h1>

<p class="lead">The Right Mix - ​Tinkering + Engineering + Language</p>

<p>The DSKI Summer Camp is a specially designed camp for curious makers to construct, tinker and engineer, with a strong focus on developing ​soft skills​ and ​independence​.</p>
<p>In an intentionally set-up space, makers will learn to manage their time, resources and ideas while having fun, working out ways to ​solve problems as they create exciting projects through ​experimentation​ and ​discovery​.</p>
<p>A linguistic component has been added to our camp this year to provide a fun platform for creative expression.</p>
<p>ONLY 24 PLACES AVAILABLE, JOIN US FOR A SUMMER OF POSSIBILITIES!</p>

