<h2 class="mt-4">Description</h2>

<h5>WEEK ONE - Dingle Dangle Puppets</h5>
<p>Explore the world of puppetry, develop linguistic skills, write original scripts and stage a puppet show.<br>
Field Trip : Muji+ Creative Studio</p>

<h5>WEEK TWO - Movers and Shakers</h5>
<p>Design circuits, code games, build and code a robot, design a robot maze and create other movable projects.<br>
Field Trip : Kawasaki Good Times World</p>

<h5>WEEK THREE - Work with Wood</h5>
<p>Use tools safely to construct with wood, use design thinking to create practical pieces, integrate technology and circuitry into finished projects.<br>
Field Trip : Takenaka Carpentry Tools Museum</p>

<h5>WEEK FOUR - Out of the Box</h5>
<p>Indulge in creative cardboard construction, build movable automation, understand how gears work and create a mechanical toy.<br>
Field Trip : Arimata Toys and Automata Museum</p>

